# 004 Add Submission Status API

Status: Proposed

## Objective

Extend the controller with a submission-scoped status endpoint.

The controller already exposes aggregate status across all work. This slice adds a new API that reports the execution state of a single submitted workflow.

The new endpoint becomes the controller interface used by future `goet status`, `--wait`, and `--watch` functionality.

